cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper uses Internet search engine queries to predict drug recalls, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves data mining and machine learning techniques to analyze the search query data, which falls under sub-categories such as cs.SI (social and information networks), cs.SD (databases), and cs.CR (learning). Finally, the paper deals with healthcare and pharmaceuticals, which could fall under cs.CY (computers and society).
